    <h1 class="post-h1">How to Store Reseller Inventory at Home</h1>

    <p class="post-lead">
      Closets, totes, shelves, spare rooms — home resellers store inventory everywhere.
      Here's a simple system that prevents sold items from disappearing.
    </p>
  </div>

  <hr class="post-rule">

  <h2>Start with one rule</h2>
  <p>Every item needs one location.</p>

  <h2>Use real-life location names</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Closet shelf 2</li>
    <li>Blue tote (top)</li>
    <li>Spare room rack</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="note-card post-note">
    <div class="note-title">Quick note</div>
    <p class="note-text">
      You don't need SKUs or warehouse systems.
      The goal is simply to know where the item is.
    </p>
  </div>

</article>

